<reference
    xmlns="http://docbook.org/ns/docbook"
    version="ghub-docbook-1.0"
    xmlns:xi="http://www.w3.org/2001/XInclude"
    xmlns:xlink="http://www.w3.org/1999/xlink"
    xml:id="ref.docProcess"
    xmlns:m="http://ghub.sourceforge.net/ns/model"
    xmlns:mpro="http://ghub.sourceforge.net/ns/model-profile"
    mpro:spem="http://www.omg.org/spec/SPEM/20070801/SPEM%202.0%20UML%202%20Profile.xmi"
    >

<!--

Note that this document describes part of a way to loosely couple a DocBook XML documemt to the SPEM metamodel's UML profile, as in developing an approach for a combined document-driven and model-driven design and engineering practice.

